      • syncCollection

        public <T,C extends java.util.Collection<T>> C syncCollection(C initial,
                                                              com.cleanroommc.modularui.utils.serialization.IByteBufSerializer<T> serializer,
                                                              com.cleanroommc.modularui.utils.serialization.IByteBufDeserializer<T> deserializer)
        从接口复制的说明: UISyncer
        Syncs the elements of the collection to the internal buffer.
        On the server, elements are serialized in the order of iteration.
        On the client, elements are deserialized in the same order and re-added to the collection. The list will be modified on the client
        指定者:
        syncCollection 在接口中 UISyncer
        类型参数:
        T - collection element's type
        C - the collection type itself
        参数:
        initial - collection whose elements should be synced
        serializer - serializer to write an element to the buffer
        deserializer - deserializer to read the elements to add them back to the collection
        返回:
        the synced collection

      • syncArray

        public <T> T[] syncArray(T[] initial,
                         com.cleanroommc.modularui.utils.serialization.IByteBufSerializer<T> serializer,
                         com.cleanroommc.modularui.utils.serialization.IByteBufDeserializer<T> deserializer)
        从接口复制的说明: UISyncer
        Syncs the elements of the array to the internal buffer.
        On the server, elements are serialized in the order of iteration.
        On the client, elements are deserialized in the same order.
        The array will not be modified, instead copied
        指定者:
        syncArray 在接口中 UISyncer
        类型参数:
        T - element type
        参数:
        initial - array whose elements should be synced
        serializer - serializer to write an element to the buffer
        deserializer - deserializer to read the elements to add them back to the collection
        返回:
        on the server, the initial array, otherwise the synced array copy
